Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.03,0:00:00.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:06.19,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:12.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:24.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:30.54,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.54,0:00:32.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:36.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.06,0:00:43.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:44.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:46.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:49.30,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.25,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.11,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:01.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.89,0:01:05.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.42,0:01:06.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:14.12,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:16.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.05,0:01:19.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:26.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.61,0:22:33.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:37.38,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:44.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.19,0:22:49.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:55.56,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:57.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:01.29,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.29,0:23:08.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:16.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:22.47,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.47,0:23:27.60,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:38.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:44.12,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:48.20,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.20,0:23:52.24,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:56.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.91,0:01:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你长大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听毕娜可说了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.63,0:01:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了人体炼成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今你回来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经没有你的立身之处了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么烧了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.49,0:02:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我决定了不再回头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了表示我们的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不想再看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逃避不堪回首的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想掩盖自己所犯下的过错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和晚上尿床的小孩把床单藏起来是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃避了 爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我年轻的时候一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和以前完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不早点回来？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朵莉夏一直在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕娜可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子们炼成的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是朵莉夏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有形成人形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不能说是朵莉夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说 眼睛的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说那不是朵莉夏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了制作完全无关的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.89,0:04:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个孩子失去了身体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用吃饭睡觉 一直能动？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 只要这个印记完好无损的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全就是不老不死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是装了个不定时炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴利说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来不同人之间的灵魂和肉体是无法相容的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬是放到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会产生拒绝反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那会是明天还是10年后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 不马上恢复原来的身体就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.73,0:05:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 如果觉得身体不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把灵魂转移到别的东西上继续生存吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使维持现状
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也感受不到疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不需要食物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个身体不是很方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温莉 我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 每次都是哥哥或者温莉先生气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都没机会生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来这个身体无法睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够恢复原来的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还回来 我弟弟的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我唯一的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给你？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把弟弟变成那种身体的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华·艾尔利克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.20,0:06:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈不要这种身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德 还在睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你父亲要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能拿走这张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四个人一起照的只有这张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:29.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为回礼 告诉你一个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家马上要发生很糟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.86,0:07:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃去别的国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕的事情又不少见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些小家伙把这里当作归宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说我没忠告过你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.79,0:08:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也回来吃个饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 毕娜可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计再也吃不到你做的饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要把那个挖出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要停手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手脚的衔接处在痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要下雨了 快点做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.14,0:09:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不确认的话就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆 妈妈的头发是棕色才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腿骨 太长了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨盆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是男人的骨盆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是你母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 死去的人无法复生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是真理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.65,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保持清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始 这就是绝望的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 现在却和希望相连
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔能取回身体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.57,0:12:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这是卡迪斯家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 是爱德吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.02,0:12:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有件事想问师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么 给我说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:44.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是师傅进行人体炼成的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和阿尔炼成的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:13:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 你到底想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅炼成的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是师傅的小孩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:27.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子们在战场上好好干了一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍恩海姆到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 他什么也没说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个重要的口信要给他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口信？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是朵莉夏的遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个人回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能替我告诉他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法遵守约定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定？是什么约定？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 如果遇到那家伙替我转告他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.66,0:14:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看他那个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是很关心你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揍他一拳之后我再转告他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回中央都市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 去被阿尔臭駡一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.81,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一个人干了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然坏成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 出了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人造人 刽子手巴利？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有无法相容的身体和灵魂之间的拒绝反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把剩下的铠甲拉长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔能取回原来的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了能恢复就能恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在利塞布尔 我把那时我们炼成的东西挖出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为 为什么做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从结果来说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.94,0:16:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,判明了那个不是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.55,0:16:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:12.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们炼成了完全不同的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 我获得了能取回你身体的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在谈这个话题之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.34,0:16:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温…温莉 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是否记得我们兄弟俩因为谁要娶你而吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前在屋顶上说过的话题？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你把阿尔甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 甩了 甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 有事要问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甩了他的理由是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要比我身高还低的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别用身高决定男人的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 这和阿尔的身体有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.57,0:17:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 阿尔知道我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的事情温莉也记得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说那是真正存在的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.32,0:17:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为记得真正存在的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以固定在铠甲上的是真正的阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.80,0:17:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那扇门里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.19,0:17:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只有灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是把你成功地拉出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果灵魂能拉出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也应该能把肉体从门里拉回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和灵魂分离 并且肉体还存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刽子手巴利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔 想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拉进真理之中的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.07,0:17:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:17:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以和灵魂一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把肉体也拉出来就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从被认为是妈妈的那个东西里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里面的 原来是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是因为拒绝反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂没有固定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.17,0:18:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候 我们没有伤害任何人的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.37,0:18:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔利克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米·卡迪斯小姐打来的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我调查了我的家谱和丈夫的家谱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.25,0:18:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼成出来的孩子的肤色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:52.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我们夫妇之间无法产生的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你查到什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:19:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复阿尔身体的信心和…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让死去的人复生是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是缺少什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是做不到的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:16.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说了“谢谢”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天开始就一直在责备自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把妈妈变成那种样子的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.72,0:19:59.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有杀死妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊兹米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有第二次杀死那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我把你的身体变成了那样是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管做什么 我都要把你的身体恢复…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赞同了那种做法的我也是同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别老是满口自己一个人来背负的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.28,0:20:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管什么都自己一个人背
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不想再因为自己的事情而让别人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休斯先生也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当知道他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在想 如果要牺牲别人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使不恢复身体也行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看过许多 即使有着不是人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.01,0:21:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也以自己的风格活着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是这种身体 周围的人也把我当人一样对待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.28,0:21:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是定时炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活生生的身体也一样会有预料不到的生老病死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 想普通地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体也没有任何不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.87,0:21:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经能这样想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再度过独自一人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想恢复身体的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 让我们干一场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.48,0:22:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踢飞真理那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把你的身体拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的背影有那么高大吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.77,0:24:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤同伴的身影
